import React from 'react';
import {
Footer,

Bars,

} from './FooterElements';

const Navbar = () => {
return (
	<>
	<Nav>
		<Bars />

		<NavMenu>
		<NavLink to='/about' activeStyle>
			About
		</NavLink>
		<NavLink to='/events' activeStyle>
			Events
		</NavLink>
		<NavLink to='/nowplaying' activeStyle>
			Now Playing
		</NavLink>
		<NavLink to="/bookmovie" activeStyle>
			Book Movie
		</NavLink>
		<NavLink to='/comingsoon' activeStyle>
			Coming Soon
		</NavLink>
		<NavLink to='/cafe' activeStyle>
			Cafe
		</NavLink>
		<NavLink to='/sign-up' activeStyle>
			Login or Sign Up
		</NavLink>
		</NavMenu>
	</Nav>
	</>
);
};

export default Footer;
